## Core Technologies
- **React 19.1.0** for UI components
- **TypeScript 5.8.3** for type safety
- **Tailwind CSS 4.1.7** for styling with custom design system
- **WXT 0.20.6** for browser extension development
- **Zustand 5.0.5** for state management
- **Google Generative AI 1.0.1** for content processing
- **Framer Motion 12.12.1** for animations
- **Dexie 3.2.4** for local database management

## Architecture Highlights
- **Shadow DOM**: Isolated UI injection to prevent conflicts with YouTube
- **Content Script**: Runs on all web pages with YouTube-specific functionality
- **Multi-browser Support**: Chrome and Firefox compatibility
- **Real-time Communication**: WebSocket integration for live AI interactions
- **Local Storage**: Persistent note storage with topic organization
